HEADWORD: Debating
<hw>De*bat"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of discussing or
arguing; discussion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Debating society</b></col> <it>or</it>
<col><b>Debating club</b></col></mcol>, <cd>a society or club for the
purpose of debate and improvement in extemporaneous
speaking.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Debatingly</ent>⟦br⟧
